1
00:00:00,960 --> 00:00:04,059
Are you Yang Hyeji?

2
00:00:04,060 --> 00:00:05,660
What?

3
00:00:06,860 --> 00:00:09,360
<i> [The Witch Store]</i>

4
00:00:11,260 --> 00:00:14,830
<i> [Episode 3] 
 [A Rival Spurs a Love Triangle]</i>

5
00:00:21,240 --> 00:00:23,880
<i> I can't stand it any longer.</i>

6
00:00:28,440 --> 00:00:30,896
What am I supposed to do if you suddenly appear at school?

7
00:00:30,896 --> 00:00:32,680
Didn't I tell you that I would be going?

8
00:00:32,680 --> 00:00:34,319
Then, you really came?

9
00:00:34,319 --> 00:00:38,240
- Who took care of the shop during the day? 
 - We are not busy during the day anyway.

10
00:00:38,240 --> 00:00:40,816
Don't say that like you stayed here during the night.

11
00:00:40,816 --> 00:00:44,656
Right. Guess how bored I am without any customers coming in.

12
00:00:44,656 --> 00:00:46,940
Who would go to school just out of boredom?

13
00:00:46,940 --> 00:00:50,440
Well, I'll continue going for a little while. So let's get along, please.

14
00:00:50,440 --> 00:00:52,836
Oh, speak casually at school.

15
00:00:52,836 --> 00:00:55,180
We are the same age there.

16
00:00:56,260 --> 00:00:59,600
Fine. However, please make sure you follow some rules.

17
00:00:59,600 --> 00:01:00,776
Let me hear what they are first.

18
00:01:00,776 --> 00:01:04,576
First, your identity as a witch should be kept secret.

19
00:01:04,576 --> 00:01:05,640
Okay.

20
00:01:05,640 --> 00:01:09,036
Second, don't use your power at school.

21
00:01:09,036 --> 00:01:12,040
A witch is not supposed to use her power?

22
00:01:12,040 --> 00:01:15,000
Okay, fine.

23
00:01:15,000 --> 00:01:20,740
- Thirdly... 
 - You don't want me to tease Yuho.

24
00:01:20,740 --> 00:01:22,240
Okay.

25
00:01:22,240 --> 00:01:26,280
I just kidded around with him today. He is not my type.

26
00:01:26,280 --> 00:01:29,936
Anyway, please make sure to follow these three rules.

27
00:01:29,936 --> 00:01:31,519
Fine, that's easy.

28
00:01:31,519 --> 00:01:33,860
There's nothing else, right?

29
00:01:33,860 --> 00:01:35,739
Like what?

30
00:01:35,739 --> 00:01:38,260
My business is in trouble.

31
00:01:38,260 --> 00:01:40,156
I could sell these at school.

32
00:01:40,156 --> 00:01:42,840
Fourth, don't do any business activity at school.

33
00:01:43,400 --> 00:01:47,200
You are too bad. Too bad!

34
00:01:56,520 --> 00:01:59,576
Yuho, are you having fun with Youngji these days?

35
00:01:59,576 --> 00:02:01,496
It's not like that.

36
00:02:01,496 --> 00:02:03,740
You gave her my chocolate milk.

37
00:02:03,740 --> 00:02:06,840
- Your milk? 
 - Oh, it's over.

38
00:02:06,840 --> 00:02:09,096
Congrats!

39
00:02:09,096 --> 00:02:10,880
Focus.

40
00:02:13,000 --> 00:02:17,260
- You missed it.
 <i>- You are not qualified to be a top athlete in class. You are really bad.</i>

41
00:02:17,720 --> 00:02:21,640
Oh, would you mind passing the ball to us?

42
00:02:24,480 --> 00:02:26,416
Who is that?

43
00:02:26,416 --> 00:02:29,099
- Here! 
 - Thank you.

44
00:02:29,100 --> 00:02:32,400
- Do you want to play? 
 - No, thank you.

45
00:02:32,400 --> 00:02:36,720
- I haven't seen him before. 
 - He is in class 2 so you may not know him.

46
00:02:36,720 --> 00:02:39,680
- Focus! 
 - Block him. Block him.

47
00:02:45,240 --> 00:02:47,560
Oh, Hye...

48
00:02:47,580 --> 00:02:50,680
- Do you need a hand? 
 - What?

49
00:02:52,920 --> 00:02:55,656
You are in class 1, right? I can carry these there.

50
00:02:55,656 --> 00:02:58,739
- Oh, I am fine. 
 - No, I can do it for you.

51
00:02:58,739 --> 00:03:02,420
- My class is next to yours. 
 - Thanks.

52
00:03:02,420 --> 00:03:07,040
- Are you Yang Hyeji? 
 - What?

53
00:03:07,820 --> 00:03:11,760
I'm right. It is you. It's been a while.

54
00:03:11,760 --> 00:03:14,816
- Do you know me? 
 - You don't remember me?

55
00:03:14,816 --> 00:03:18,036
I am Yoon Sungwoo. I used to live next door.

56
00:03:18,036 --> 00:03:21,436
Yoon Sungwoo? You transferred when you were in elementary school!

57
00:03:21,436 --> 00:03:24,836
I've come back. You have not changed at all.

58
00:03:24,836 --> 00:03:27,060
Really? Do you attend this school?

59
00:03:27,060 --> 00:03:30,340
- Do you still do judo? 
 - Yeah.

60
00:03:30,340 --> 00:03:32,056
This school is famous for its judo team.

61
00:03:32,056 --> 00:03:34,416
Oh, yeah. Where do you live now?

62
00:03:34,416 --> 00:03:35,879
- Now... 
 - Hyeji.

63
00:03:35,880 --> 00:03:37,700
Oh, Yuho.

64
00:03:38,720 --> 00:03:41,999
He is Yoon Sungwoo. He used to live next door. He transferred to class 2.

65
00:03:41,999 --> 00:03:44,976
- This is Han Yuho. He is my classmate. 
 - Nice to meet you.

66
00:03:44,976 --> 00:03:47,036
- I saw you at the gym earlier, right? 
 - Yeah.

67
00:03:47,036 --> 00:03:50,120
Right. Nice to meet you.

68
00:03:50,120 --> 00:03:52,620
- This... 
 - No! I'm fine.

69
00:03:53,280 --> 00:03:56,380
- Hyeji, let's go. 
 - Okay.

70
00:03:56,380 --> 00:03:57,896
Let's go, Yuho.

71
00:03:57,896 --> 00:04:00,800
<i> Shouldn't I have been between them?</i>

72
00:04:01,480 --> 00:04:04,356
That gym boy and Hyeji are friends?

73
00:04:04,356 --> 00:04:06,960
Class 2... who?

74
00:04:06,960 --> 00:04:09,780
- Sungwoo. 
 - Sungwoo?

75
00:04:09,780 --> 00:04:12,280
Oh, Yoon Sungwoo?

76
00:04:12,280 --> 00:04:14,440
Do you know him?

77
00:04:14,440 --> 00:04:16,916
He transferred and got a full score at the September mock test as soon as he got here.

78
00:04:16,916 --> 00:04:20,060
Oh, so what?

79
00:04:20,060 --> 00:04:23,800
Yeah, what would you know about that?

80
00:04:24,260 --> 00:04:27,596
What's more interesting is that he is specialized in judo.

81
00:04:27,596 --> 00:04:31,016
Oh, really? He is too competent.

82
00:04:31,016 --> 00:04:33,076
I don't even feel like studying anymore.

83
00:04:33,076 --> 00:04:35,679
- Let's go to the internet cafe. 
 - Okay, let's go.

84
00:04:35,679 --> 00:04:38,280
Yeah, why don't we...

85
00:04:38,280 --> 00:04:40,920
No thanks. You guys enjoy. I'll study.

86
00:04:40,920 --> 00:04:44,299
- Hey, why? 
 - Let's go.

87
00:04:44,299 --> 00:04:46,639
- Yuho, let's go. 
 - No thanks.

88
00:04:46,639 --> 00:04:49,079
Let's go, Yuho.

89
00:04:49,079 --> 00:04:50,940
Let's go!

90
00:04:50,940 --> 00:04:56,260
I should play Jungle Teemo. Let's go just this once.

91
00:04:56,260 --> 00:04:57,979
Oh, hey, block him.

92
00:04:57,979 --> 00:05:01,296
- Hey, Baron! Baron is coming. 
 - I have Gangta here.

93
00:05:01,296 --> 00:05:04,879
Why would you use Moondo for Gangta? What a waste.

94
00:05:04,879 --> 00:05:07,296
Hey, focus. Stop them from coming in.

95
00:05:07,296 --> 00:05:09,296
Taeil, Yuho is taking the back.

96
00:05:09,296 --> 00:05:11,936
Hey, where are you going, fools?

97
00:05:11,936 --> 00:05:14,300
Okay.

98
00:05:14,300 --> 00:05:16,919
- Wow, the diamond class is excellent. 
 - Awesome.

99
00:05:16,919 --> 00:05:18,739
Yuho, save me!

100
00:05:18,739 --> 00:05:20,780
- One more? 
 - Let's go.

101
00:05:22,260 --> 00:05:25,720
Hey, is that...

102
00:05:25,720 --> 00:05:27,476
Oh, such a top student comes here.

103
00:05:27,476 --> 00:05:29,840
Hey, what tier is he at?

104
00:05:29,840 --> 00:05:33,480
- Never mind. Why? 
 - Silver?

105
00:05:33,480 --> 00:05:35,800
Oh, wait. He is going to charge money.

106
00:05:35,800 --> 00:05:38,700
I am going to patrol.

107
00:05:42,680 --> 00:05:44,959
Why? What?

108
00:05:44,959 --> 00:05:46,840
Silver?

109
00:05:48,820 --> 00:05:52,760
- Challenger. 
 - What?

110
00:05:55,280 --> 00:05:57,940
Oh, Yuho.

111
00:05:57,940 --> 00:06:00,496
- Hi. 
 - Hi.

112
00:06:00,496 --> 00:06:02,416
You are Challenger—

113
00:06:02,416 --> 00:06:04,676
No, I mean Yoon Sungwoo. I am Park Hyungseok.

114
00:06:04,676 --> 00:06:07,859
Hey you're Sungwoo, right? I am Choi Taeil.

115
00:06:07,859 --> 00:06:11,920
My tier is gold... bronze which is like gold.

116
00:06:11,920 --> 00:06:13,739
Would you join us if you are alone?

117
00:06:13,739 --> 00:06:16,079
Oh, the computer is on. Come here.

118
00:06:16,079 --> 00:06:17,836
Do you like sausage with rice cake?

119
00:06:17,836 --> 00:06:19,880
What is going on here?

120
00:06:31,500 --> 00:06:34,196
You did so good.

121
00:06:34,196 --> 00:06:36,480
Can I call you Professor?

122
00:06:36,480 --> 00:06:39,220
No, no. I haven't played for so long.

123
00:06:39,220 --> 00:06:42,436
Wow, professor! You are Challenger!

124
00:06:42,436 --> 00:06:44,156
You are humble.

125
00:06:44,156 --> 00:06:46,516
Yuho is a good player too.

126
00:06:46,516 --> 00:06:50,800
Hey, he is way lower than you.

127
00:06:50,800 --> 00:06:53,460
Be quiet, bronze.

128
00:06:53,460 --> 00:06:56,480
Oh, yeah. I heard that you know Hyeji.

129
00:06:56,480 --> 00:06:59,356
Right. I used to live next door.

130
00:06:59,356 --> 00:07:00,636
Okay.

131
00:07:00,636 --> 00:07:02,876
You do judo? How long have you been doing it?

132
00:07:02,876 --> 00:07:05,179
Well, I started it when I was young.

133
00:07:05,179 --> 00:07:07,110
I am not too good at it.

134
00:07:07,540 --> 00:07:11,060
Well, Yuho does judo too.

135
00:07:11,060 --> 00:07:13,199
What are you talking about?

136
00:07:13,200 --> 00:07:15,760
Really? You do judo?

137
00:07:15,760 --> 00:07:18,879
- Well... 
 - He was a prospective player.

138
00:07:18,879 --> 00:07:21,220
- Hey, what are you talking about? 
 - Speaking of that...

139
00:07:21,220 --> 00:07:23,396
- You have a photo of doing judo at home. 
 - That is...

140
00:07:23,396 --> 00:07:25,880
Come visit our judo team.

141
00:07:27,020 --> 00:07:30,516
- What? The judo team? 
 - Yeah.

142
00:07:30,516 --> 00:07:33,500
Yuho must start practicing today.

143
00:07:35,020 --> 00:07:37,680
Okay, I will go later.

144
00:07:38,760 --> 00:07:41,399
Hey, Taeil, you shouldn't have said that.

145
00:07:41,399 --> 00:07:43,699
Why? It was all true.

146
00:07:43,700 --> 00:07:46,556
- You used to do judo. 
 - Just two months in elementary school. That's all.

147
00:07:46,556 --> 00:07:48,576
Exactly, it's not like you never did it.

148
00:07:48,576 --> 00:07:51,260
Hey, why did you tell him about the photo?

149
00:07:51,260 --> 00:07:53,256
I saw it. You have it in your house, right?

150
00:07:53,256 --> 00:07:56,496
My mom took it when I was young. That's all.

151
00:07:56,496 --> 00:07:59,720
How would I know such details?

152
00:07:59,720 --> 00:08:01,779
- What should I do? 
 - Just don't go.

153
00:08:01,779 --> 00:08:03,499
No! You have to go.

154
00:08:03,500 --> 00:08:07,396
- If you don't visit him, you'll admit your loss. 
 - What are you talking about?

155
00:08:07,396 --> 00:08:10,836
Oh, yeah. You promised to visit him.

156
00:08:10,836 --> 00:08:13,796
Yuho could win.

157
00:08:13,796 --> 00:08:16,980
- I trust you. 
 - Right. You are a source of our pride.

158
00:08:16,980 --> 00:08:20,436
- Fighting! 
 - You two really are of no help to me.

159
00:08:20,436 --> 00:08:23,376
- Yuho, fighting! 
 - Fighting!

160
00:08:23,376 --> 00:08:25,040
We're going.

161
00:08:30,080 --> 00:08:32,120
I'm ruined.

162
00:08:34,620 --> 00:08:38,740
Oh, what is that? 
 <i>[The Witch Store]</i>

163
00:08:38,740 --> 00:08:40,950
<i>[Contract] </i>

164
00:08:41,680 --> 00:08:45,436
Oh, you don't believe me? Why do I have to sign a contract?

165
00:08:45,436 --> 00:08:48,576
I can't trust you. Hurry up and sign it.

166
00:08:48,576 --> 00:08:51,460
Okay, I will do it later.

167
00:08:55,160 --> 00:08:57,000
Is it a cafe?

168
00:08:58,700 --> 00:09:00,140
What?

169
00:09:09,560 --> 00:09:12,580
<i> Why is he here?</i>

170
00:09:21,710 --> 00:09:25,090
Welcome. I have been waiting for you.

171
00:09:30,660 --> 00:09:34,460
<i> [Shoes That Let You Jump High]</i>

172
00:09:34,460 --> 00:09:37,140
♫ <i> It's moving in your direction </i> ♫

173
00:09:37,140 --> 00:09:42,000
Sungwoo can we play duo from time to time?

174
00:09:42,000 --> 00:09:44,616
Of course. Call me whenever you want to.

175
00:09:44,616 --> 00:09:46,896
Wow, you are so generous. You want more food?

176
00:09:46,896 --> 00:09:49,456
- What do you want? 
 - I only want something to drink.

177
00:09:49,456 --> 00:09:52,236
- Okay, I got it. 
 - Get me chocolate milk.

178
00:09:52,236 --> 00:09:54,510
Hey, you just go with plain water.

179
00:09:54,510 --> 00:09:59,210
♫ <i> I understood what you were </i> ♫

180
00:09:59,210 --> 00:10:01,060
♫ <i> Can you feel it coming tonight? </i> ♫

181
00:10:01,060 --> 00:10:03,260
He won't buy you anything.

182
00:10:03,260 --> 00:10:05,400
I know.

183
00:10:05,400 --> 00:10:08,240
I will work hard to be Challenger by next week.
